1. The Eye 
5. Feeling 
At Sāvatthī. 
“Mendicants, feeling born of eye contact is impermanent, perishing, and changing. 
Feeling born of ear contact, 
feeling born of nose contact, 
feeling born of tongue contact, 
feeling born of body contact, 
and feeling born of mind contact are impermanent, perishing, and changing. 
Someone who has faith and confidence in these principles is called a follower by faith. …” 
